<div class="one-third column">
  <div class="shimmed">
    <h3>Cone Patrol?</h3>
    <p>I heart skiing.  I double heart skiing powder.  "Cone Patrol" is a term a ski buddy gave to hiking the cone at <a href="http://mtbachelor.com">Mt. Bachelor</a> prior to opening for freshiez.</p><p>Born from that tradition is <em>conepatrol.com</em>, a way for you &ndash; the fellow shredder, to get powder alerts sent to your phone via text.</p>
    <p>So ditch the snow phone, and setup a <em>conepatrol</em> alert to shout at you when the goods have dropped.  See you on the cone &ndash; or up at the Doo, or Mt. Hood Meadows too!</p>
    <p>&ndash; @conepatrolapp</p>
  </div>
</div>
  <div class="one-third column">
    <div class="shimmed">
    <h3>How it Works</h3>
    <ul class="square">
      <li><p><strong>Ullr Delivers</strong>: Someday (soon) it will snow once again up in the Cascades.  As you slumber, lord Ullr will take a massive dump on your favorite ski hill!</p></li>
      <li><p><strong><em>conepatrol</em> Texts</strong>: The trusty Cone Patrol robot scours the interwebs for the latest freshiez measurements.  Unlike your ski bro partner, the cp robot doesn't drink too many jaeger bombs and then pass out and forget to look at conditions.</p></li>
      <li><p><strong>Make Turns</strong>: If there is enough freshies to suit your fancy at your ski hill of choice, we send you a text.  You gear up, get stoked, and git sum.  No need to call the snow phone, or view a web page, you get notified when the gnar has arrived.</p></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="one-third column">
    <div class="highlight shimmed">
      <% if !shredder_signed_in? -%>
    <h3>Sign Up!</h3>
    <p>Signing up is super simple, and free!  Fill out this form, and we'll send you a confirmation text.  Its as easy as snowboarding!</p>
    <p>Enter your mobile number (10 digits no dashes/spaces), and select the new snow threshold to trigger an alert.</p>
    <%= form_for @shredder do |f| %>
      <%= f.label :email %>
      <%= f.text_field :email %>
      <%= f.label :password %>
      <%= f.password_field :password %>
      <%= f.label :password_confirmation %>
      <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %>
      <%= f.label :mobile, 'Mobile:' %>
      <%= f.text_field :mobile %>
      <%= f.label :mobile, 'Freshies Threshold:' %>
      <%= f.select :inches, (2..12).collect{|i| ["#{i} or more inches",i]}, {:include_blank => false} %>
      <%= f.label :area_id, 'Ski Area:' %>
      <%= f.select :area_id, Area.active.collect{|i| [i.name,i.id]}, {:include_blank => false} %>
      <%= f.submit 'Sign Up', {:id=>'sign_up'} %>
    <% end %>
  <% else -%>
    <h3>Yo <%= current_shredder.random_name %>!</h3>
    <% if current_shredder.confirmed? -%>
    <div class="shimmed stat">
      <span class="title"><a href="/subscriptions">Your Subscriptions</a></span>
      <span class="value"><a href="/subscriptions"><%= current_shredder.active_subscriptions.size -%></a></span>
    </div>
    <div class="shimmed stat">
      <span class="title">Alerts Sent</span>
      <span class="value"><%= current_shredder.alerts.size -%></span>
    </div>
    <% else -%>
    <p>We need to confirm your mobile number before we can send alerts.  Click the button below to confirm you number (<%= current_shredder.mobile %>):</p>
    <a href="/confirm" class="button">Confirm Now</a>
    <% end -%>
  <% end -%>
  </div>
  </div>
